## Djot Individual tags

This contains following tags:

- Headings
- Paragraphs
- Line breaks
- Emphasis
- Blockquotes
- Lists
- Code blocks
- Images
- Links and Horizontal rules
- Tables
- Task Lists (not supported)
- Strikethrough
- Mixed
